05\/allah-multiplies-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4107,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Allah multiplies reward for spending charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone gives charity from what is good, for Allah only accepts what is good, except that the Merciful takes it with His right hand. Even if it is a date, it is nurtured in the hand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/04\/be-fair-merciful-keep-promises\/","url_meta":{"origin":4107,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Virtue: Be fair, be merciful, and keep your promises","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you judge, be just. When you make a covenant, keep it. When your mercy is sought, be merciful. Whoever does not do any of that, the curse of Allah, His angels, and all people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20166,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/13\/debt-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":4107,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Debts: Allah merciful to lenitent creditor","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfa reported: 